# School Portal Web Project
Update cursor rules on everyupdate for maintaining the firestore rules and firebase data with app and website

## Project Overview

A comprehensive web portal for schools to manage teachers and students. The platform allows schools to register, create accounts for teachers and students, and manage user access.

## Features

- School registration with name, code, email, and password
- School login via email and password
- Teacher management (add by email, generate passwords)
- Student management (add by roll number, name, username,generate password)
- Secure authentication with Firebase
- Responsive design for all device sizes

## Technology Stack

- Frontend: Next.js, React
- Authentication: Firebase Authentication
- Database: Firebase Firestore
- Mobile App (Future): React Native with Expo
- State Management: React Context API
- Styling: Tailwind CSS

## Development Phases

1. Phase 1: School Portal Website

   - School authentication (signup/login)
   - Dashboard for schools
   - Teacher and student management

2. Phase 2: Mobile App
   - Login for teachers and students
   - Classroom features
   - Notifications
   - Integration with web portal

## Current Focus

Building the web portal for schools with complete authentication and user management functionality.
